1.System can take any file that contains a valid  text content
2.Extract the Text Content
  tools available-http://tika.apache.org/
3.Summarize the extracted text using the summarizer configured by the user
  Eg:-http://knowitall.cs.washington.edu/gflow/
      http://autosummarizer.com/
4.Quantify and report the match of the created summary with computer science domain(previously created word2vec model* for the domain can be used for this)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Creating Word2Vec Model for the domain-:
1.Crawl Open Url Directory For Computer Science and Collect as much as text content related to computer science
  (http://www.dmoz.org/Computers/Computer_Science/)
2.Create  WORD2VEC model for the text content extracted
  http://radimrehurek.com/gensim/index.html	

